metadata.name: Depths of The Soul
metadata.description:
"Geai had been dead for two thousand three hundred and forty-two days when she began to smile. That smile, at the beginning, no one to see it. What happens to the things that no one sees? They grow. Everything that grows grows in the invisible and takes, over time, more and more strength, more and more space. to shed more and more light."

This collection Inspired by "Geai" which written by Christian Bobin

technic: Digital Mixed Media 

illustrator & Motion by elham monsef
